Actions to comply with the selected priority are set out in the Latvian National Development Plan 2021-2027: https://www.pkc.gov.lv/sites/default/files/inline-files/NAP2027_apstiprin%C4%81ts%20Saeim%C4%81_1.pdf 
For example:
1. Education economic growth;
2. Nature and Environment - Green Course;
3. Nature and Environment - Green Course;
4. A cohesive, safe and open society

Contact details of the team responsiblle for open data activities are availabble at MEPRD home page, Latvian Open data porrtal contacts are available on portal website, also contact details of the SRDA experts are available on the SRDA website.

